Math problem:
 A circle is circumscribed around $ABCD$ as follows: [asy]
pair pA, pB, pC, pD, pO;
pO = (0, 0);
pA = pO + dir(-40);
pB = pO + dir(40);
pC = pO + dir(130);
pD = pO + dir(190);
